int var;
{0} << "Please enter a value \n";
{1} >> var;

quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Accepting User Input [/h1]

You can accept user input multiple times throughout the program: [code format="cpp" codeId="937"]#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
    int a, b;
    cout << "Enter a number \n";
    cin >> a;
   [b] [/b]cout << "Enter another number \n";
    cin >> b;

    return 0;
}[/code]

quizzes.question:
